phil’s new merch, right

it’d be cool if dan wore it too. why not.

great colour combination. psychologically, yellow and black together give a feeling of unease (as i know), but fcиk it. still my favourite combination, besides red n black and orange n black. what am i even ranting about, there are loads of gorgeous colour schemes.

don’t ask me bout that glowing thing i don’t know either feel free to drop your guesses

if u look closer, probably can notice fishnets. in three places. what a cheeky detail *awkward wink*

plz don’t repost it without credits ⭐
